	<Title>
		Sagging breasts: Inevitable after breast-feeding?
	</Title>
	<Abstract>
		Sagging breasts are more likely after pregnancy, but breast-feeding isn&apos;t necessarily a contributing factor.
	</Abstract>
	<Question>
		Are sagging breasts inevitable after breast-feeding?
	</Question>
